  &lt;li&gt;Assisting in customer configuration and setups for special ticketing events and programs&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Be part of an initial launch team for testing and quality assurance; perform basic setup and configuration management and liaise with internal delivery teams.&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Performing training services via web-conferencing and in-person&lt;/li&gt;
